com.camerontec.catalys.server.adapter.ouch.cache

Interface OrderCache

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MarketMirrorOrderCache

    public interface OrderCache
    Interface to be implemented by classes which can provide information about order for OUCH Adapter and be able to link order to corresponding incoming FIX message and OUCH specific details.
